a^2, b^2, c^2
c^2-b^2=b^2-a^2
c^2=2b^2-a^2
(2b-a)^2=2b^2-a^2
4b^2-4ab+a^2=2b^2-a^2
2b^2-4ab+2a^2=0
2b^2+2a^2=4ab
2b^2-4ab+2a^2=0
b^2-2ab+a^2=0
(b-a)^2=0
(b-a)^2=0
b-a=0
